{"tid":1392403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支援前線","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T18:03:52.000Z","uid":113998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"199e0b572f33de45335f008f5b96c37487b415d3","tid":1392403,"uid":113998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:24:37.000Z","msg":"我同班手足搵緊supplier大手訂full set 豬咀加碳罐for refill 亦會訂埋hardhat同goggles之後送上前線 有幾樣野需要幫手<br />\n<br />\n1 除左個頭 仲有咩裝備係有需要<br />\n2 有冇手足可以幫手做運輸<br />\n3 有冇真正前線收發點提供<br />\n4 有冇手足想加入訂單<br />\n5 如提供食物飲品 應如何入手<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰 齊上齊落<br />\n一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e11ccb8d65ce673cf46eb253e7542e16fec42e9","tid":1392403,"uid":113998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77ac67aebdb33ab2b27d0440c5305001ee501cec","tid":1392403,"uid":113998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72b39152ab49dba90e8134ccd2f395047d0490e","tid":1392403,"uid":113998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJK0PvB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJK0PvB.jpg&h=7cec74ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db02195bc23d594d68f871e40ad2b7c63d0f0800","tid":1392403,"uid":216789,"like":